content:
Huh? {短暂停}—Huh?
Is it really that intense? {短暂停}
...I need to take another look.

Hmm...{短暂停}My apologies, I mistook you for someone else,{短暂停}
You're a friend of our Astralink contact,
I've heard about you.

About conversation topics... (thinking){短暂停}
Oh, if during your Astralink travels, you happen to see
houses with... (draws out the blade "Oddhead")

I was just having a chat with Big Gem and Little Gem.{短暂停}
...Why that puzzled look on your face?
Don't tell me the gems where you're from don't speak to you?

The calendar reads,
"Today is most suitable for staying indoors."{短暂停}
Splendid, let's go out and explore!

In fact, even as we speak,
I've already played out eight different scenarios in my mind.{短暂停}
The theme? They're all about "the return of family members."

The troubles of this season?
...{短暂停}
Shedding.

Weather's nice. Good time to hunt, yep.
What do I hunt?{短暂停}
...how about you start running?

Yee? Yeep?!{短暂停}
Yeeeeep!
Oh my... This is... I've discovered something extraordinary!

Oh, so you two were classmates,
Companions during those precious years.{短暂停}
As for me, I took quite a different path!~

{摆尾}{摆尾}{摆尾}
Yeep? My tail?
It emits a Faintglow at certain special moments.

...{思考}
Oh, how could family
be like friends?

I rarely engage in impulse purchases,
except when it comes to painting supplies and tools,{短暂停}
they always give me this reassuring sense of confidence.

Hello, I'm <color=#8AAB4B>Medowlyn</color>,
a fashion color coordination enthu...{短暂停}
professional coordinator. Delighted to meet you, darling~.

About conversation topics... (thinking){短暂停}
Oh, you must be curious about
Strange tales and mysterious things.

Oh my, a visitor I haven't seen before.
You must be the contact's friend, yes?{短暂停}
Our contact is quite popular indeed.

About conversation topics... (thinking) {短暂停}
I've been working on
some new creative projects lately.

About our conversation topic... (contemplating){短暂停}
I'm still thinking about it,
Let's discuss it next time.
